title: Dr. Jake Deutsch
description:
In this episode Ellen sits down with the owner and clinical director of Oakwood Precision Medicine Dr. Jake Deutsch. They discuss biohacking, continuous glucose monitors, and how subtle long term changes can make a big difference in your health journey.
